<div id="main-div">
    <div class="columns">
        <div id="playlists-column" class="column">
            {{#each playlists}}
            <div id="playlist-element">
                <a href="/playlists/{{id}}/songs">
                    <div class="card" style="background-color: black; min-height: 10vh">
                        <header class="card-header" style="color:white">
                            <div class="media">
                                <div class="media-left">
                                    <figure class="image is-48x48">
                                        <img src="https://bulma.io/images/placeholders/96x96.png"
                                            alt="Placeholder image">
                                    </figure>
                                </div>
                                <div class="media-content">
                                    <p class="title is-4">{{name}}</p>
                                    <p class="subtitle is-6">{{username}}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </header>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
        <div id="column-information" class="column">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="media">
                        <div class="media-left">
                            <figure class="image is-48x48">
                                <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/34190754?s=460&u=8889cfd4e58b27e2a58785c567d32287aca39eff&v=4"
                                    alt="Placeholder image">
                            </figure>
                        </div>
                        <div class="media-content">
                            <p class="title is-4">NextGenerationWeb</p>
                            <p class="subtitle is-6">by Camille Maurel</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content">
                        <p>NextGenerationWeb project is a Streaming plateform like Spotify and Deezer.</p>
                        <cite>"As project work you will create a platform where users can create and share music
                            playlists. Users will be able to create accounts, playlists and then add songs to their
                            playlists. A playlist can be either private (only the user who created it can see it) or
                            public (anyone can see it)."</cite>
                        <br><br>
                        <img src="https://wakatime.com/badge/github/MagnasiePro/NextGenerationWeb.svg">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    #main-div {
        background: rgb(25, 20, 20);
        background-image: linear-gradient(#c074b2, #8ab5e8);
    }

    #playlist-element {
        margin: 10px 0;
        width: 35vw;
    }

    .columns {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff00, #000000de 50%);
        padding: 20px 50px;
        min-height: 100vh;
    }

    #github-avatar {
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .avatar {
        display: inline-block;
        overflow: hidden;
        vertical-align: middle;
        border-radius: 6px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    #column-information {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }
</style>